u]]'' (2010) as Sexton Geevarghese\n* ''[[Elsamma Enna Aankutty]]'' (2010) as Karippalli Sugunan\n* ''[[Thanthonni]]'' (2010) as Kochouseppu & Thankachan\n* ''[[Brahmasthram (2010 film)|Brahmasthram]]'' (2010) as MLA Vasudevan\n* '' [[Kadaaksham]]'' (2010)\n* '' [[Janakan]]'' (2010)\n* '' Chitrakuzhal'' (2010)\n* ''[[Alexander the Great (2010 film)|Alexander The Great]]'' (2010)\n* ''[[Pokkiri Raja (2010 film)|Pokkiri Raja]]'' as 'Kaavi' Krishnan (2010)\n* ''[[Puthiya Mukham]]'' (2009)\n* ''[[Red Chillies (film)|Red Chillies]]'' (2009)\n* ''[[Black Dalia]]''( 2009) as  IG Mathew K. John\n* ''Hailesa'' (2009)\n* ''I G'' (2009)\n* ''Samayam'' (2009)\n* ''[[Kana Kanmani]]'' (2009)\n* ''[[Chattambinadu]]'' (2009)\n* ''[[Decent Parties]]'' (2009)\n* ''[[Swantham Lekhakan]]'' (2009)\n* ''Patha Nilayile Theevandi'' (2009)\n* ''[[Daddy Cool (2009 Malayalam film)|Daddy Cool]]'' (2009)\n* ''[[Ee Pattanathil Bhootham]]'' (2009)\n* ''[[Angel John]]'' (2009) as Jaimes\n* ''Oru Pennum Randaanum'' (2008)\n* ''[[Sultan (2008 film)|Sultan]]'' (2008) as Shivasankara Pilla\n* ''[[Twenty:20 (film)|Twenty:20]]'' (2008) as Balan\n* ''Roudram'' (2008)\n* ''Kanal Kannadi'' (2008)\n* ''Innathe Chinthavishayam'' (2008)\n* ''[[Nasrani (film)|Nasrani]]'' (2007) as M. C. Paul\n* ''Naalu Pennungal'' (English title: ''Four Women'') (2007)\n* ''[[Sooryan (2007 film)|Sooryan]]'' (2007) as Simon Thekkilakkadan\n* ''4 July'' (2007) as Gopalan\n* ''[[Big B (film)|Big B]]'' (2007) as George\n* ''[[Chotta Mumbai]]'' (2007) as Mohandas\n* ''[[Vinodayathra]]'' (2007) as Rajappan\n* ''[[Speed Track]]'' (2007) as Chandradas\n* ''Sketch'' (2007) as Alexander Namad\n* ''Mouryan'' (2007)\n* ''[[Avan Chandiyude Makan]]'' (2007) as Chandi\n* ''Mayavi'' (2007) as Thottappally Surendran\n* ''Inspector Garud'' (2007) as Karaikudi Arumukha Chettiyar\n* ''[[Chacko Randaaman]]'' (2006) as Devanarayan\n* ''Chess'' (2006) as Devarajan\n* ''Kilukkam Kilukilukkam'' (2006) as Krishnadas\n* ''Rashtram'' (2006) as Medayil Ch